254
00:17:23,900 --> 00:17:25,000
Au revoir.

255
00:17:33,100 --> 00:17:34,100
Alors...

256
00:17:34,800 --> 00:17:36,600
Asseyez-vous.

257
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:45,200
- C'est un sacré personnage.
