447
00:29:07,700 --> 00:29:10,200
"des types à triste mine

448
00:29:10,900 --> 00:29:12,600
"bourrés dans les latrines".

449
00:29:12,600 --> 00:29:14,100
C'est pas mignon ?

450
00:29:14,300 --> 00:29:16,100
Très.

451
00:29:17,400 --> 00:29:18,900
J'ai un secret.

452
00:29:20,300 --> 00:29:22,200
Mais je dois m'approcher
pour vous le dire.

453
00:29:22,200 --> 00:29:23,200
Non.

454
00:29:24,800 --> 00:29:26,000
Me...

455
00:29:26,500 --> 00:29:28,400
- Reculez.
- ... voilà.

456
00:29:28,600 --> 00:29:29,600
Femme.

